[13:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'technical but very insightful. So, let\'s go over this in simple terms. You see, one of the biggest challenges of making image generation models today is that it\'s really hard to create a single model that can do everything from text'

[13:15] [scene:talk]
