AUDIO: 'often very different skills that require different parameters and can often interfere with one another. Well, how dance OPD works is that instead of blending together multiple specialist models and hoping they cooperate, the'

[14:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'researchers treat each capability as its own separate field that the student model can learn from individually. Basically, think of every expert model as a teacher with a unique specialty. Rather than asking all the teachers for'

[14:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'advice at once, which can result in conflicting instructions, dance OPD picks just one teacher for each training example. The student asks the teacher what it should do at that current point during image generation and simply'

[14:27] [scene:talk]
